1
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:29,950
[The Story of Xing Fu]

2
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:33,050
[Episode 23]

3
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:40,959
Here.

4
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,040
You guys should check the second clause.

5
00:01:42,319 --> 00:01:43,040
And those below it.

6
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:45,319
Mr. Guan and the rest

7
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,359
came all the way here

8
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,599
to resolve this case.

9
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,760
Dear villagers.

10
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,359
Please listen to Mr. Guan for now.

11
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,599
This case

12
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,000
is clear

13
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,959
from the start.

14
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,680
Actually,

15
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,519
this is just a contract breach.

16
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,920
Our main issue now

17
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,920
is to provide the court

18
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,319
with solid evidence.

19
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,879
That evidence

20
00:02:07,239 --> 00:02:09,240
will be the contracts you had.

21
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,360
Oh.

22
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:13,199
And an accurate marker of your losses.

23
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,240
All of these

24
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,719
can become the base

25
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,319
that we can use to request compensation

26
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:19,080
from them.

27
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,879
We cannot guarantee our win.

28
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,479
However, I think

29
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,319
we have a huge chance of winning.

30
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,240
Does everyone

31
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,120
still have the contract?

32
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,800
Yes.

33
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,159
I have it.

34
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:31,800
I left it at home.

35
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,400
I didn't bring it.

36
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,520
-Mine is gone.
-You didn't bring it?

37
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,439
-Calm down.
-It's missing.

38
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,199
Those

39
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:36,120
who have their contracts with them,

40
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,280
if you're willing,

41
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,520
you can

42
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,000
sign

43
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,599
the letter of attorney with our lawyers here.

44
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,280
Our lawyers

45
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,000
will press charges against them

46
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,080
on our behalf.

47
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,000
As for those without the contract,

48
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,960
you guys can calm down.

49
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,879
Go home and search for it.

50
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,400
If you truly can't find it,

51
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,080
you guys can

52
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,560
find evidence

53
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,439
of your cooperation with the other party
for the past few years

54
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,240
and show them to us.

55
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,080
So, what can be considered evidence?

56
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,039
It's

57
00:02:58,639 --> 00:02:59,240
the bank statement

58
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,520
that consists

59
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,479
of your transaction

60
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:02,840
with

61
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:03,960
the other party.

62
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:06,479
It's fine as long it can prove
that you worked together

63
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,280
with the other party.

64
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,439
Okay?

65
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:10,080
So, first,

66
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,039
let's deal with those

67
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,159
who have the contracts with them.

68
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,759
Next, we'll deal with those

69
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,159
who don't have the contracts with them,

70
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:16,919
okay?

71
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:17,840
Okay.

72
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,800
Alright.

73
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:20,560
So,

74
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,439
is there anything else?

75
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,719
There's one more thing

76
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,199
we need to tell you guys beforehand.

77
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,039
We have

78
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:25,879
to tell you guys

79
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:26,919
about our standard rate.

80
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,719
Next,

81
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:28,080
let us

82
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,560
invite Mr. Zhang to speak.

83
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,560
Here.

84
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:31,719
Dear villagers,

85
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,360
let me tell you guys about our rate.

86
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:36,159
According to the regulations of our law firm,

87
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,120
we usually

88
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:40,680
charge at least 2,000 yuan per case

89
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,360
for contract disputes such as these.

90
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,080
It's that expensive?

91
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,680
However...

92
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,280
That's too expensive.

93
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:47,520
However,

94
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,560
we do

95
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,240
take your difficulties

96
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,560
into account.

97
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:54,000
That's why we've prepared two solutions today.

98
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,120
First,

99
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,479
if you hand over the contract right now,

100
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:00,080
we'll charge you

101
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,759
1,500 yuan per case.

102
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,199
That's okay.

103
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:03,319
1,500 yuan isn't too bad.

104
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,879
There's a second solution.

105
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,319
Second,

106
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,479
we'll charge

107
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,280
you guys

108
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,159
for

109
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,360
a contingency fee.

110
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,520
What's that?

111
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,439
We'll only take the money

112
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:14,479
if we win the case.

113
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:15,919
However,

114
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,079
due to the risk,

115
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,279
we have to charge a higher rate.

116
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,199
We'll charge

117
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,480
4,000 yuan per case.

118
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,720
That's why

119
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,839
you guys

120
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,360
can consider

121
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,800
the two solutions

122
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:29,560
and pick one.

123
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,600
Okay?

124
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,160
I'll take the 1,500 yuan option.

125
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:36,639
Xingfu,

126
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:38,120
decide for us.

127
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,160
Which solution should we choose?

128
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:39,639
Yeah.

129
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:40,240
Xingfu,

130
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,120
you have to help us out.

131
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:42,839
How can

132
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,040
-we afford 4,000 yuan?
-It's like this.

133
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:44,959
You see,

134
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:46,079
those established law firms

135
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,160
charge people

136
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,199
tens of thousands of yuan from the start.

137
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:49,639
No one is willing

138
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,480
to charge a low rate

139
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,439
like Mr. Guan and the rest

140
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,279
in order to help us out.

141
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,920
It's tough for the law firm too.

142
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,959
They came all the way here to help us out.

143
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,560
They need petrol for their vehicles

144
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,439
and food for themselves too, am I right?

145
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,920
All of those cost money.

146
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,759
And, we don't know how long
the court case will last.

147
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,519
[Legal counsel]
We can't just let them make a trip for nothing.

148
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:06,120
Am I right?

149
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:06,639
She has a point.

150
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:07,959
You guys should think about it.

151
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:08,839
Xingfu,

152
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,120
if so, we'll follow your advice.

153
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:10,800
I'll hand it over right now!

154
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:11,839
I'll pay 1,500 yuan.

155
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,560
Me too!

156
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,360
Us too!

157
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,560
Tell us how to pay.

158
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,079
Well...

159
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:18,800
It's like this.

160
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,040
So,

161
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:22,160
to my right is Mr. Wang.

162
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,360
Over here.

163
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,519
Those who want to go for the contingency plan

164
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,079
may go to Mr. Wang.

165
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:30,199
To my left is Mr. Zhang.

166
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,319
Those who want to go for the normal route

167
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,240
may go to him.

168
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,519
Okay.

169
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,600
I'll sign it now.

170
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,399
I'll pay right now.

171
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:38,680
Remember to read the agreement first.

172
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:39,519
Okay!

173
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,079
Everyone!

174
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:40,839
Queue up!

175
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,480
Queue up!

176
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,519
Calm down.

177
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,800
Take your turns.

178
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,879
Dear villagers,

179
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:47,120
please queue up.

180
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,439
Take your turns.

181
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,519
Don't panic.

182
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:50,480
Don't panic.

183
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:51,959
It's fine.

184
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,040
You guys can search for it at home.

185
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:54,720
If you guys

186
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:56,319
couldn't find it...

187
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,079
Qinglai?

188
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,680
Qingzhi?

189
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,199
What are you doing here?

190
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:08,800
You...

191
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,879
What are you doing?

192
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,079
I was preparing dinner.

193
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,279
Your sister-in-law

194
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,560
is working in the city.

195
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,439
She's doing great.

196
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,800
She went on a business trip

197
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,439
with the other lawyers.

198
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,560
I had to cook for myself.

199
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:19,920
Fine.

200
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,240
I bought some takeaways.

201
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,079
You should stop cooking.

202
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:22,879
Let's eat together.

203
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,360
Not bad, brat.

204
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,120
Sure.

205
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,199
Come on.

206
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:39,800
Qinglai,

207
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:40,879
it's rare for the house to be quiet.

208
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,319
Today,

209
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,199
we have to drink.

210
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,319
Qinglai,

211
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,000
without you,

212
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,279
I wouldn't get to where I am.

213
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,040
What's wrong with you today?

214
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,360
Did something happen?

215
00:06:59,360 --> 00:06:59,759
Qinglai,

216
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,439
I'm going

217
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,040
to be the secretary

218
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,680
of our city's vice mayor.

219
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:07,680
You got promoted?

220
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,959
I shouldn't think about it for now.

221
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,639
Even so, it's a fact.

222
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,759
You spent time with the superiors

223
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:15,720
all day long.

224
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,879
Of course they'll promote you

225
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:17,800
when you do a good job.

226
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:19,399
Here.

227
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:21,199
Let me offer you a toast.

228
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:22,480
Thank you, Qinglai.

229
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,079
Qingzhi,

230
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,319
I won't need to beg anyone anymore

231
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:33,560
after you get promoted.

232
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:38,800
Qinglai,

233
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,519
I just

234
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,360
got promoted.

235
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:42,800
I have

236
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,720
to be extra cautious

237
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,240
and work extra hard.

238
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,079
I will

239
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,279
never have the guts

240
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,920
to go against the law.

241
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,279
I know that.

242
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,079
You...

243
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,759
You don't need to worry.

244
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:53,920
I won't create trouble

245
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,079
for you

246
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:56,959
even if I have to starve to death.

247
00:07:58,879 --> 00:07:59,680
It's just that...

248
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,439
It's just that one of my colleagues

249
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,199
begged me

250
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,120
to ask you

251
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,759
so that you could

252
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:06,319
ask your father-in-law to get a job for him.

253
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,360
That's all.

254
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:13,040
Qinglai,

255
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,639
I was just planning

256
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:15,000
to tell you

257
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:15,600
about that.

258
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,399
Can you stop asking

259
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,279
Yani's father

260
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:18,800
for help

261
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,600
in the future?

262
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,079
Do you think I dare to ask him for help?

263
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,360
Do you know

264
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:25,959
how

265
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,399
he looked at me when I greeted him?

266
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,800
It was as if

267
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,879
I was dog poo.

268
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,159
Qinglai,

269
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,399
do you know

270
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,279
how I got to be the secretary?

271
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,799
I don't.

272
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,039
How did you get promoted?

273
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,399
First,

274
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,759
I did well in my job.

275
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:47,799
I was

276
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,759
acknowledged by my superiors.

277
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,279
However, in my opinion,

278
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,639
I wouldn't be promoted

279
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:54,519
this easily if Yani's father

280
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:55,519
didn't acknowledge me.

281
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,720
After all,

282
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,519
her father is a member

283
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:58,120
of the Municipal Council's

284
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,799
Organization Department.

285
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,279
He has the right

286
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,000
to give his opinion

287
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,360
on the appointment of all officers.

288
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:07,600
Qinglai,

289
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,240
to put it bluntly,

290
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,519
if her father

291
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:11,960
said

292
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,000
something bad

293
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,320
about me,

294
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,960
my future

295
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,840
would've been ruined.

296
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:27,600
Okay...

297
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,159
Okay.

298
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,799
If so,

299
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,000
I'll avoid him in the future.

300
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,399
Qinglai,

301
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:38,279
I...

302
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,639
Let me offer you a toast.

303
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,000
You've suffered because of me.

304
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,039
Let me offer you a toast instead.

305
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:45,080
Congratulations.

306
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:46,840
Come on.

307
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,039
Listen,

308
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,440
after we head back,

309
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:00,440
we have to win Ms. Liu's case first.

310
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,879
With that,

311
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:03,360
the rest of the cases

312
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,399
will follow suit

313
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,240
and everything will be easy.

314
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,279
There are over 20 contracts here.

315
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:17,840
We have over 30,000 yuan here.

316
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,559
And, plenty of people were still queuing up

317
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:24,960
to sign the contingency plan with us.

318
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,320
Today,

319
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,200
I've taught you guys a proverb.

320
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,799
This is what you call

321
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,519
"Many a little makes a mickle".

322
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:32,879
You better learn it.

323
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:34,879
Hey,

324
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,240
I have something to discuss with you two.

325
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:39,519
I've been thinking about this
for the past two days.

326
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,600
We just started our law firm not long ago.

327
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,080
Why are we putting on a facade?

328
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:45,519
Xingfu is of enormous help to us.

329
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,360
If she wishes to become our receptionist,

330
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:48,879
we should let her be one.

331
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,360
We should let Xingfu grow together

332
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:52,480
with our law firm.

333
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:53,360
What do you guys think?

334
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:58,720
Of course it's a yes!

335
00:10:58,879 --> 00:10:59,440
You don't say?

336
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,399
-He's hungry.
-It's cold.

337
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:02,879
It got cold.

338
00:11:02,879 --> 00:11:03,759
-Give me a second.
-Is that so?

339
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,519
Let me heat it.

340
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,399
Time to eat.

341
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,120
Mom,

342
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:09,759
Dad.

343
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:11,120
Xingfu?

344
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,440
When did you come back?

345
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:15,159
I followed Mr. Guan and his men
to Shiqiao Village for a business trip.

346
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,360
We passed by on our way back to the city.

347
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,399
That's why I applied for leave

348
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,440
to visit you guys

349
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:19,480
and Little Dou.

350
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,120
Here.

351
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,799
Here's your mother.

352
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,240
Dou.

353
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,519
Look at Mommy.

354
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,559
Do you still recognize me?

355
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,000
Do you miss Mommy?

356
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:33,679
It'll be terrifying if he can speak.

357
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,120
Mom.

358
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:36,519
Good boy.

359
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:37,879
Dad, it must've been tough on both of you.

360
00:11:39,399 --> 00:11:40,639
When we're more able,

361
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:42,960
we'll bring Dou to the city

362
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,799
and let him attend kindergarten.

363
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,039
You guys can relax by then.

364
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,879
Dou is the source of our lives.

365
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:48,399
We'll be disheartened

366
00:11:48,399 --> 00:11:49,759
if you bring him away.

367
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,519
This is your mother.

368
00:11:59,519 --> 00:12:00,399
Your mother is here.

369
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,279
Mr. Wan.

370
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:15,559
Who's there?

371
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:18,759
Who is it?

372
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:20,279
I'm here to visit you.

373
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,039
Xingfu, you're here?

374
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:23,320
Let me help you up.

375
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,080
It's fine.

376
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:24,600
It's totally fine.

377
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,600
Hey.

378
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:29,679
-Why did you bring so much stuff?
-I bought something for you.

379
00:12:29,759 --> 00:12:30,159
I...

380
00:12:30,159 --> 00:12:32,080
I don't know what to buy before I visit you.

381
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,360
You're too courteous.

382
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,159
Have a seat.

383
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:35,679
Here.

384
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,159
You don't need to be so courteous.

385
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:39,840
I'm not being courteous at all.

386
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,120
I even ate

387
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,360
the old hen you gave me.

388
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:44,360
You still remember that?

389
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,320
So,

390
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,000
Qinglai,

391
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:47,759
how is he doing?

392
00:12:48,159 --> 00:12:49,399
Qinglai is working in the city.

393
00:12:50,519 --> 00:12:51,360
In the past,

394
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:53,120
I made a promise to your mother-in-law.

395
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:54,799
I said

396
00:12:54,879 --> 00:12:55,919
I would let

397
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:56,759
Qinglai

398
00:12:56,759 --> 00:12:57,840
work in the factory.

399
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,320
That promise

400
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:00,559
still counts.

401
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,519
You guys can come back

402
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:03,960
anytime you like.

403
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:04,960
Mr. Wan,

404
00:13:06,279 --> 00:13:08,000
thank you for still remembering us.

405
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,320
Regarding that issue...

406
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:12,559
Let's

407
00:13:13,159 --> 00:13:13,799
forget about that.

408
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,039
Even if

409
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:16,399
you were pressing charges against me,

410
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,960
you were still doing the right thing.

411
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,360
I didn't do my job well.

412
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:21,840
Mr. Wan,

413
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,639
it all happened

414
00:13:23,639 --> 00:13:24,279
because

415
00:13:24,279 --> 00:13:25,440
I wrote the letter.

416
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,519
I've let you down.

417
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:28,240
Hey, Xingfu.

418
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:28,840
Get up.

419
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,919
You don't need to do that.

420
00:13:30,039 --> 00:13:30,639
Sit down.

421
00:13:32,639 --> 00:13:33,320
Xingfu,

422
00:13:34,159 --> 00:13:35,039
I've given the issue

423
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:36,559
some thought as well.

424
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,639
You're a good child.

425
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,840
I

426
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,120
admire

427
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:42,840
your drive,

428
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,720
your honesty,

429
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:46,039
your reasonable demeanor,

430
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:46,919
and your kindness.

431
00:13:48,519 --> 00:13:49,639
You should work hard out there.

432
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,720
You shouldn't forget about Wan Village

433
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:54,720
even after you've made it big.

434
00:13:57,399 --> 00:13:58,480
You should

435
00:13:58,919 --> 00:13:59,399
contribute

436
00:13:59,440 --> 00:13:59,960
to Wan Village too.

437
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,000
But of course.

438
00:14:02,679 --> 00:14:03,879
I'm a member of Wan Village.

439
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,240
I will never leave my roots behind

440
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,240
no matter how far I go.

441
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,279
Don't worry.

442
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:09,960
You're a good child.

443
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:11,639
I will

444
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:13,240
remember your words.

445
00:14:18,372 --> 00:14:24,725
[Receptionist: He Xingfu]

446
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:32,840
Hey.

447
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,879
Seems like our new receptionist

448
00:14:34,879 --> 00:14:35,840
isn't too pleased

449
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,720
with her new job.

450
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,799
Looks like she's upset.

451
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,639
Of course I'm upset.

452
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,279
You guys tease me all day long.

453
00:14:41,399 --> 00:14:41,919
Look.

454
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:42,840
You never take my words seriously.

455
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,399
Why are you suspecting us?

456
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:45,639
Come on.

457
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:47,240
Let us welcome

458
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,519
our new receptionist,

459
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,720
Ms. He Xingfu.

460
00:14:51,279 --> 00:14:53,159
You guys should stop teasing me.

461
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:55,039
Who's trying to tease you here?

462
00:14:55,039 --> 00:14:55,559
Xingfu,

463
00:14:55,559 --> 00:14:56,399
do we look like swindlers

464
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:57,639
to you?

465
00:14:57,919 --> 00:14:58,679
Yeah.

466
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,080
You two should stop.

467
00:15:02,679 --> 00:15:04,559
You're our new receptionist.

468
00:15:04,559 --> 00:15:05,919
Do you two spoil moods for a living?

469
00:15:06,039 --> 00:15:06,600
Huh?

470
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,279
The news was good,

471
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,120
but you two made it

472
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,039
seem like a scam.

473
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:13,879
Ms. He Xingfu,

474
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,399
we plan

475
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,480
to recruit you

476
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:18,480
as the receptionist of Fangyuan Law Firm.

477
00:15:19,279 --> 00:15:20,399
From now on, you will

478
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,200
receive

479
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:22,960
3,000 yuan per month.

480
00:15:23,559 --> 00:15:24,720
If there's no objection...

481
00:15:24,848 --> 00:15:25,960
[Fangyuan Law Firm]

482
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,159
you may sign here

483
00:15:27,519 --> 00:15:28,360
after reading the contract.

484
00:15:30,679 --> 00:15:31,200
What?

485
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:31,919
Here.

486
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:36,240
Is...

487
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,080
Is this for real?

488
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,039
Of course.

489
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:38,919
Am I...

490
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,120
Am I a real receptionist now?

491
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:40,679
Yeah.

492
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:41,720
Keep up the good work.

493
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,039
This is so sudden.

494
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:44,840
By the way,

495
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:45,720
I'm still working

496
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,480
as the handyman, right?

497
00:15:47,519 --> 00:15:48,120
I'll come here

498
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:48,840
one hour earlier

499
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,120
and leave half an hour later every day.

500
00:15:50,679 --> 00:15:51,559
Can you do it?

501
00:15:51,679 --> 00:15:52,799
Of course!

502
00:15:53,799 --> 00:15:54,279
After that?

503
00:15:54,279 --> 00:15:55,120
Do you have any other requests?

504
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:55,600
I...

505
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,039
Since I'm doing two jobs at once,

506
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:57,720
I...

507
00:15:58,480 --> 00:15:59,639
I won't ask for much.

508
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,759
I just

509
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,879
want an additional 500 yuan

510
00:16:02,879 --> 00:16:03,399
per month.

511
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,159
3,500 yuan will be fine.

512
00:16:09,519 --> 00:16:10,000
However,

513
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,360
you shouldn't celebrate yet.

514
00:16:11,919 --> 00:16:13,480
Although you've graduated

515
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,200
from being a handyman,

516
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,600
being a receptionist

517
00:16:15,919 --> 00:16:17,240
is something new to you.

518
00:16:17,919 --> 00:16:18,840
We'll give you a three-month probation period.

519
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,679
If you don't

520
00:16:19,679 --> 00:16:20,600
do a good job at it,

521
00:16:21,140 --> 00:16:22,100
you will return

522
00:16:22,100 --> 00:16:23,100
to being a handyman.

523
00:16:23,530 --> 00:16:24,410
No problem!

524
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:25,260
You can do it!

525
00:16:31,169 --> 00:16:37,275
[Signature of Party B: He Xingfu]

526
00:16:47,650 --> 00:16:48,170
Hey!

527
00:16:48,290 --> 00:16:49,020
I'm back!

528
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:51,410
That's fine and all,

529
00:16:52,140 --> 00:16:53,410
but why did you have to scare me?

530
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:54,100
Did you strike the lottery?

531
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:55,500
I'm a receptionist now.

532
00:16:57,890 --> 00:16:59,020
Although I'm still working as a handyman too,

533
00:16:59,690 --> 00:17:01,050
I'll receive 3,500 yuan per month now.

534
00:17:01,930 --> 00:17:02,620
That way,

535
00:17:02,770 --> 00:17:03,740
if we add both of our wages

536
00:17:03,770 --> 00:17:04,260
together,

537
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:05,610
we'll have at least 6,000 yuan per month.

538
00:17:05,940 --> 00:17:07,570
They're giving you an extra 2,000 yuan per month?

539
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:08,130
Yeah.

540
00:17:10,810 --> 00:17:11,460
Mr. Liu,

541
00:17:12,090 --> 00:17:12,530
I will

542
00:17:12,530 --> 00:17:13,050
have

543
00:17:13,050 --> 00:17:13,940
1 kg of pork ribs.

544
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:15,460
I want this,

545
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:15,740
this,

546
00:17:15,740 --> 00:17:16,260
and this.

547
00:17:20,370 --> 00:17:20,900
Xingfu.

548
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:22,460
Yani.

549
00:17:22,460 --> 00:17:22,940
You're here.

550
00:17:23,770 --> 00:17:24,570
Come in.

551
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:25,220
Okay.

552
00:17:25,610 --> 00:17:26,020
Yani is here.

553
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:26,570
Hello, Qinglai.

554
00:17:26,570 --> 00:17:27,260
Do the dishes

555
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,050
for me.

556
00:17:28,810 --> 00:17:29,980
Sure, you guys can have a chat.

557
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:31,850
Let me hold this for you.

558
00:17:32,090 --> 00:17:32,500
Xingfu,

559
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,810
this is the outfit I bought for you.

560
00:17:33,810 --> 00:17:35,260
You should try them and see if they fit you.

561
00:17:35,850 --> 00:17:37,130
Yani, you bought things for us again.

562
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,770
Don't be so courteous with me.

563
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:40,610
I'll get upset if you do so.

564
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:42,980
Look at what I've bought for you.

565
00:17:44,220 --> 00:17:45,180
I didn't buy any

566
00:17:45,180 --> 00:17:46,660
heavy makeups for you

567
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:46,980
because

568
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:47,850
we could not put on heavy makeup

569
00:17:47,850 --> 00:17:48,980
during work.

570
00:17:49,050 --> 00:17:50,090
That's why

571
00:17:50,090 --> 00:17:51,090
I bought some light makeup for you.

572
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:52,770
You can try the color later.

573
00:17:53,130 --> 00:17:53,570
Okay.

574
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:54,570
Xingfu, have a seat.

575
00:17:56,770 --> 00:17:57,770
Bring me the mirror.

576
00:17:57,770 --> 00:17:58,370
Try this.

577
00:18:06,740 --> 00:18:07,500
But, Xingfu,

578
00:18:10,220 --> 00:18:10,980
one's elegance

579
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:12,900
is more than just putting on makeup

580
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:13,610
and dressing oneself nicely.

581
00:18:13,810 --> 00:18:14,940
I need to study too.

582
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:16,260
I know that.

583
00:18:16,980 --> 00:18:18,420
Wisdom in hold, elegance in mold.

584
00:18:19,130 --> 00:18:20,050
What was that again?

585
00:18:22,740 --> 00:18:24,020
What I meant was

586
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:24,610
when you have

587
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:25,130
enough knowledge,

588
00:18:25,130 --> 00:18:26,290
your elegance

589
00:18:26,290 --> 00:18:27,530
will flow out naturally.

590
00:18:28,810 --> 00:18:29,660
Not just that,

591
00:18:30,050 --> 00:18:30,900
we need to be confident

592
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:32,020
and polite too,

593
00:18:33,130 --> 00:18:33,700
am I right?

594
00:18:33,810 --> 00:18:35,050
Xingfu,

595
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:35,940
you've totally changed.

596
00:18:36,660 --> 00:18:37,810
